I am a polyglot.

16
00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:58,159
Well I feel really impressed and a bit intimidating.

17
00:00:59,119 --> 00:01:02,159
And now Hannah we always start our programme off with a question.

18
00:01:02,799 --> 00:01:04,159
